verses.text:
To wit, the two pillars, and the pommels, and the chapiters
which were on the top of the two pillars, and the two wreaths to cover the two pommels of the chapiters which
were on the top of the pillars;

And Solomon made all the vessels that
were for the house of God, the golden altar also, and the tables whereon the shewbread
was set;
